The or is the top division of and is the top professional association football
league in Japan. It is one of the most successful leagues in Asian club football
and the only league given top class 'A' ranking by the AFC. Currently, J.League
Division 1 is the first level of the Japanese association football league
system. The second tier is represented by J. League Division 2.
